.panel-container
  .panel.students-bg
  h1.title = t ".headline"
  p.white.subtitle = t ".subtitle"
.white-bg
  .spacer-small
  .row
    .small-12.medium-9.columns
      p#hook
        | We are an organization of passionate UC Berkeley students
        | who develop web and mobile applications for non-profit organizations.
        | As a member, you will be able to join a family of likemineded students
        | working to use our education and technological prowess to make the
        | world a better place.
    #apply-button.small-12.medium-3.columns
      - if @settings.student_app_open
        = link_to "Apply Now", new_student_application_path, class: "button"
      - else
        .applications-closed
          p Applications are now closed for this semester. Thank you for your interest!
  .spacer-small
.gray-bg
  .spacer-large
  .row
    .title-column
      h1 Application Process
    .content-column
      .small-12.columns
        ul.timeline-vertical
          li.work.timeline-row
            .relative
              h5.title Infosessions
              span.date/
              h5 TBA
              span.circle
            .timeline-content
              p
                | Come out and talk to us
                | to learn more about Blueprint at one of our infosessions.
          li.work.timeline-row
            .relative
              h5.title Applications Due
              span.date/
              h5 TBA
              span.circle
            .timeline-content
              p
                | Fill out the online application. Our inital cuts will be based
                | on the application and will be emailed out ASAP.
          li.work.timeline-row
            .relative
              h5.title Blueprint Games
              span.date/
              h5 TBA
              span.circle
            .timeline-content
              p
                | A fun little event for you guys
                | to flex your problem solving muscles in a team of other applicants. Second round
                | cuts will be based on this event.
          li.work.timeline-row
            .relative
              h5.title Behavioral Interviews
              span.date/
              h5 TBA
              span.circle
            .timeline-content
              p
                | The final step in the applicaiton process, we really want to feel your passion for social good
                | in person. Final decisions will be announced from this event.
      .small-12.columns.decision-criteria
        .spacer-small
        h4.title Decision Criteria
        p If we could, we would accept every applicant but unfortunately we cannot manage the volume of people and administrative overhead while still fulfilling our mission to the best of our abilities. The following criteria are what we use to evaluate applicants.
        ul
          li
            strong Passion
            p This is the single most important criteria. Do you demonstrate a genuine passion for social good?
          li
            strong Skill
            p Do you have the necessary skills to productively contribute to the mission?
          li
            strong Experience
            p Do you have relevant work experience? Volunteering experience?
          li
            strong Attitude
            p Do you demonstrate positive, hard-working attitude?
          li
            strong Teamwork
            p Do you display the ability to work well in a team?
          li
            strong Culture
            p Will you get along well with the rest of Blueprint? We’re sure you will!
